That's my understanding Sophie.
To overcome problems with the CampaignFlow website needing the information transferred to be so exact, eg address with domain ID, agents details only in the format they have set up etc, we chose to do a work around. That takes the details created in our quote platform and only transfers it to CampaignFlow in their notes field, rather than prepopulating the name/agent fields on their platform. It does mean customers need to re input details on the CF platform. We thought that was not ideal, but reasonable as they are completing a loan application
David
